casebody.data:
Realty Income Properties 24, L.L.C.
v.
Delaware Cty. Bd. of Revision 2016-1427 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 9, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

At oral argument before a master commissioner on June 19, 2018, the parties in this case indicated that they have reached a settlement. Within 14 days, the parties shall file either an application for dismissal or a notice of failure of settlement.
